# [[.AppName]]

A Go web application built with hexagonal architecture and generated by [scaffold](https://github.com/esrid/scaffold).

[[if eq .APIMode "ssr"]]**Stack:** html/template В· HTMX В· Tailwind CSS (CDN) В· [[if eq .DB "postgres"]]PostgreSQL[[else]]SQLite[[end]] В· Chi router[[end]][[if eq .APIMode "rest"]]**Stack:** JSON REST API В· Chi router В· [[if eq .DB "postgres"]]PostgreSQL[[else]]SQLite[[end]] В· TypeScript/esbuild[[end]][[if eq .APIMode "grpc"]]**Stack:** REST JSON + gRPC В· Chi router В· [[if eq .DB "postgres"]]PostgreSQL[[else]]SQLite[[end]] В· protobuf[[end]]

## Getting started

```bash
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env вЂ” set DATABASE_URL and SECRET_KEY at minimum
make run
```

[[if eq .APIMode "rest"]]Server runs on `:8080`. Add models with `scaffold gen`:

```bash
scaffold gen Product name:string! price:float! description:string
# в†’ GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/products
```
[[end]][[if eq .APIMode "ssr"]]Server runs on `:8080`. Add models with `scaffold gen`:

```bash
scaffold gen Product name:string! price:float! description:string
# в†’ /products  (list, show, create, edit pages)
```
[[end]][[if eq .APIMode "grpc"]]HTTP server on `:8080`, gRPC on `:50051`. Add models with `scaffold gen`:

```bash
scaffold gen Order status:string! total:float!
make proto   # compile .proto в†’ Go pb package
# в†’ /api/orders (REST) + gRPC ProductService
```
[[end]]

## Project structure

```
internal/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ core/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ domain/       # structs, Validate(), error types
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ ports/        # repository and service interfaces
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ services/     # business logic
в””в”Ђв”Ђ adapters/
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ http/         # [[if eq .APIMode "ssr"]]SSR handlers, bindForm[[else]]JSON CRUD handler[[end]]
    в”њв”Ђв”Ђ store/        # SQL queries[[if eq .APIMode "grpc"]]
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ grpc/         # gRPC handlers, translateError[[end]][[if ne .APIMode "grpc"]]
    в””в”Ђв”Ђ store/        # SQL queries (last entry, no grpc)[[end]]
internal/app/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ app.go            # server startup, route mounting
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ config.go         # env-based config
в””в”Ђв”Ђ registry.go       # dependency wiring (auto-regenerated)
[[if eq .APIMode "ssr"]]web/templates/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ layout.html       # header/footer partials
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ home.html
в””в”Ђв”Ђ {model}/          # list.html, form.html, show.html (auto-generated)
[[end]][[if eq .APIMode "rest"]]web/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ src/              # TypeScript + CSS source
в””в”Ђв”Ђ dist/             # built assets (committed for zero-build deploys)
[[end]][[if eq .APIMode "grpc"]]api/proto/v1/
в””в”Ђв”Ђ {model}.proto     # auto-generated, compile with: make proto
[[end]]```

## scaffold commands

```bash
# Add a new model
scaffold gen Article title:string! body:string! views:int

# Add a field to an existing model (generates ALTER TABLE migration)
scaffold gen Article title:string! body:string! views:int published:bool!

# Remove a model
scaffold destroy Article

# Preview without writing
scaffold gen Article title:string! --dry-run
```

## Field types

| Type | Go | SQL |
|------|----|-----|
| `string!` | `string` | `TEXT NOT NULL` |
| `string` | `*string` | `TEXT` |
| `int!` | `int` | `INTEGER NOT NULL` |
| `float!` | `float64` | `REAL NOT NULL` |
| `bool!` | `bool` | `INTEGER NOT NULL` |
| `time!` | `time.Time` | `DATETIME NOT NULL` |
| `json!` | `json.RawMessage` | `TEXT NOT NULL` |

Useful modifiers: `{unique}`, `{index}`, `{default=value}`, `{fk=table,cascade}`, `{check=expr}`.

## What scaffold manages vs. what's yours

| File | Ownership |
|------|-----------|
| `domain/{model}.go` вЂ” struct fields | scaffold patches via markers |
| `domain/{model}.go` вЂ” `Validate()` | **yours** |
| `ports/{model}.go` | written once, never touched |
| `services/{model}_service_gen.go` | scaffold regenerates |
| `services/{model}_service.go` | **yours** |
| `store/{model}_store_gen.go` | scaffold regenerates |
| `store/{model}_store.go` | **yours** вЂ” add custom queries here |
| `app/registry.go` | scaffold regenerates |
| `app/app.go` вЂ” route block | scaffold regenerates |[[if eq .APIMode "ssr"]]
| `http/{model}_handler_gen.go` | scaffold regenerates |
| `http/{model}_handler.go` | **yours** |
| `web/templates/{model}/*.html` | scaffold regenerates on field changes |[[end]][[if eq .APIMode "grpc"]]
| `adapters/grpc/{model}_handler_gen.go` | scaffold regenerates |
| `adapters/grpc/shared.go` | written once |
| `api/proto/v1/{model}.proto` | scaffold regenerates |[[end]]

## Adding custom logic

**Validation** вЂ” in `internal/core/domain/{model}.go`:

```go
func (p Product) Validate() error {
    if p.Price <= 0 {
        return &domain.ValidationError{
            Entity: "Product",
            Errors: map[string]string{"price": "must be greater than zero"},
        }
    }
    return nil
}
```

**Custom queries** вЂ” in `internal/adapters/store/{model}_store.go`:

```go
func (s *ProductStore) FindBySlug(ctx context.Context, slug string) (*domain.Product, error) {
    // your SQL here
}
```

**Business logic** вЂ” in `internal/core/services/{model}_service.go`:

```go
func (s *ProductService) Publish(ctx context.Context, id string) error {
    // your logic here
}
```
[[if eq .APIMode "ssr"]]
**Extra routes** вЂ” in `internal/adapters/http/{model}_handler.go`:

```go
// Add RegisterExtraRoutes to the app.go route block manually.
func (h *ProductHandler) RegisterExtraRoutes(r chi.Router) {
    r.Get("/featured", h.Featured)
}

func (h *ProductHandler) Featured(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {
    // render a custom template
}
```
[[end]][[if eq .APIMode "grpc"]]
**After scaffold gen**, compile protos:

```bash
make proto
# Generates internal/adapters/grpc/pb/ from api/proto/v1/*.proto
```
[[end]]

## Connecting external services

New service = one interface (port) + one implementation (adapter) + wire in registry.

```
ports/storage.go      в†ђ interface  (FileStorage, Mailer, CacheвЂ¦)
adapters/s3/          в†ђ implementation
app/registry.go       в†ђ inject
```

The core never imports SDK packages. Adapters are the only place that knows about AWS, Redis, Stripe, etc.

## Environment variables

| Variable | Default | Description |
|----------|---------|-------------|
| `DATABASE_URL` | [[if eq .DB "sqlite"]]`file:app.db?_journal_mode=WAL&_foreign_keys=on`[[else]]`postgres://localhost/[[.AppName]]?sslmode=disable`[[end]] | Database connection |
| `SECRET_KEY` | вЂ” | Required вЂ” `openssl rand -hex 32` |
| `ADDR` | `:8080` | HTTP listen address |[[if eq .APIMode "grpc"]]
| `GRPC_ADDR` | `:50051` | gRPC listen address |[[end]]
| `APP_ENV` | `development` | `production` enables JSON logs + embedded assets |
| `LOG_LEVEL` | `info` | `debug`, `info`, `warn`, `error` |

